        "name": "Assistance Gap: STRUGGLING+ → ASSISTANCE_NEEDED signal",
        "metadata": {
          "description": "Fires ASSISTANCE_NEEDED when household shows moderate food strain without active food assistance enrollment — the common scenario for working families just above benefit thresholds who still face food access barriers.",
          "pattern": "STRUGGLING+",
